OL,3,CEngland qualify for World Cup knockout
OL,4,Cstages before facing Panama on Saturday
OL,6,FFans gather in Madison Square gardens
OL,7,Fahead of England vs Panama on
OL,8,FSaturday, Steve Scott reports
OL,10,FEngland's place in the knockout rounds
OL,11,Fof the World Cup has been secured
OL,12,Fahead of their final Group L game
OL,13,Fagainst Panama.
OL,15,FResults on Friday night, where Uruguay
OL,16,Fwere beaten by Spain, meant that
OL,17,FThomas Tuchel's men are assured a
OL,18,Fplace in the last 32 whatever happens
OL,19,Fagainst the Central Americans in New
OL,20,FJersey on Saturday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
