FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1782638299
OL,3,CEngland qualify for World Cup knockout
OL,4,Cstages before facing Panama on Saturday
OL,6,FEngland are guaranteed to be one of
OL,7,Fthe top eight third-placed finishers,
OL,8,Fmeaning they will progress even if
OL,9,Fthings go badly wrong against Panama.
OL,11,FBut England manager Thomas Tuchel will
OL,12,Fhave much stronger ambitions and they
OL,13,Fwill finish top of the group if they
OL,14,Fcan match Ghana's result against
OL,15,FCroatia.
OL,17,FExcitement and expectations around the
OL,18,FEuro 2024 runners-up grew after they
OL,19,Fstarted this summer's shot with a
OL,20,Fstrong 4-2 victory against Croatia in
OL,21,FDallas.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1782638299
OL,3,CEngland qualify for World Cup knockout
OL,4,Cstages before facing Panama on Saturday
OL,6,FBut Tuesday's underwhelming 0-0 draw
OL,7,Fwith Ghana dampened the mood, with
OL,8,FTuchel's side failing to find a spark
OL,9,Fin their bid to break down a low block
OL,10,Fin Boston.
OL,12,FEngland face a similar challenge in
OL,13,FSaturday's match against eliminated
OL,14,FPanama, who are 42nd in FIFA's world
OL,15,Frankings ` 23 spots higher than Ghana.
OL,17,FTuchel warned England face a "complex"
OL,18,Ffinal World Cup group game as he
OL,19,Fcontinues to seek the "recipe" to
OL,20,Fbreaking down defence-minded teams.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1782638299
OL,3,CEngland qualify for World Cup knockout
OL,4,Cstages before facing Panama on Saturday
OL,6,F"We will face another deep block in
OL,7,Fanother kind of formation," Tuchel
OL,8,Fsaid. "We now see a back five. For
OL,9,Fmany moments in the match we see a
OL,10,Fback six, we see a back seven.
OL,12,F"Normally we try to overload parts and
OL,13,Fareas in the match, try to overload
OL,14,Fand then accelerate quickly in this
OL,15,Fmoment of overload.
OL,17,F"There was no overload against Ghana.
OL,18,FThere will very likely be no overload
OL,19,Fagainst Panama."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
