PN,31205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1782638299
OL,3,CEngland qualify for World Cup knockout
OL,4,Cstages before facing Panama on Saturday
OL,6,FTuchel added: "I haven't found the
OL,7,Frecipe where 'they do this, then we do
OL,8,Fthis ` and then we are fine".
OL,10,FMore than 15,000 Three Lions
OL,11,Fsupporters are expected to travel to
OL,12,FNew Jersey for the game on Saturday,
OL,13,Fwith many taking the opportunity to
OL,14,Fcombine the trip with a sightseeing
OL,15,Ftour of nearby New York City.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
